<h4>Mission Statement</h4>
<p>BYU-Idaho Education Society is focused on providing opportunities for  students to teach and collaborate with others, while focused on  learning and mastering concepts being taught in their current classes.  It is a preparatory step in helping students prepare for a rewarding and  exciting future as teachers.</p>
<h4>Belief Statement</h4>
<ul>
<li>We believe there is no greater calling than to teach.</li>
<li>We believe by exercising faith in Jesus Christ and emulating the  examples of the Master Teacher, we can affect positive changes in  people's lives.</li>
<li>We believe teaching occurs in the home, school, church, and community.</li>
